     H            Y.
     F*** APLR07 *********************************
     F*文字数調査                              *
     F*   T.SAKASHITA               2020.08.31   *
     F********************************************
     E                    TBL       128  1
      *
     C           *ENTRY    PLIST
     C                     PARM           P@MOJI128
     C                     PARM           P@LEN   30
      *
     C                     MOVEAP@MOJI    TBL
      *
     C           1         DO   128       @C      30
     C           129       SUB  @C        @L      30
     C           TBL,@L    IFNE *BLANK
     C                     Z-ADD@L        P@LEN
     C                     LEAVE
     C                     END
     C                     ENDDO
      *
     C                     SETON                     LR
     C                     RETRN
      *
